original: Jivegård, Sven Gustaf Vilhelm, kyrkoadjunkt, Vargön, f. 2/3/13 iTo-rsö, Skarab. 1., av J. W. Johansson o. Be-da Carlsson. G. 40 m. Gunvor Johansson. Barn : Erik f. 43, Gunnar 44, Elisabet 47. — Stud:ex. i Skara 312, teol. fil. ex. 33, teol. kand. o. pra-kt. teol. prov 37, prästv. >f. Skara stift 38. Tjg. s. past :adj. i Amnehärad, stiftsadj. 40-46, kyrkoadj. i Vargön sed. 46, red. av Västgötaungd. Julbok 40-44, red. av Kyrkvägen ’sed. 43’, manuskriptförf. t. Kyrka,n mitt i byni, en smalfilm om Skara stift 46.
translated: Jivegård, Sven Gustaf Vilhelm, church curate, Vargön, b. 2/3/13 in Töresö, Skaraborg County, 1st district, son of J.W. Johansson and Be-da Carlsson. Married in '40 to Gunvor Johansson. Children: Erik b. '43, Gunnar '44, Elisabet '47. Completed high school exams in Skara in '31, theological studies in '33, theological candidate and practical theological examination in '37, ordained priest in Skara Diocese in '38. Currently serving as parish curate in Amnehärad, diocesan curate from '40-'46, church curate in Vargön since '46. Also worked as editor of the Västgötaungdernas Julbok from '40-'44, editor of Kyrkvägen from '43', and author of the manuscript for Kyrkan mitt i byn, a short film about Skara Diocese in '46.
